struct header
{
WORD data length [02: 8BYTE, 04: 16BYTE, 06: 24BYTE];
BYTE judgment related [10: Taru J, 14: Before J, 18 After J, 20: Crouching, 07: Counter 1.5 times, 26: physique judgment 3 SA eating is invalid];
BYTE technique LV related [00 ~ 1F: technique level combo correction, +20: SA production, SA judgment is different];
WORD? ;
WORD? ;
};
/ * ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ * /

/ * ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ * /
struct motion (8BYTE)
{
BYTE frame;
BYTE jump flag etc .;
WORD sound (1.5BYTE);
WORD graphic 1 (additional graphics such as slashing effect);
WORD graphic 2 (character body graphic);
};
/ * ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ * /
struct motion (16BYTE)
{
BYTE frame;
BYTE jump flag etc .;
WORD sound (1.5BYTE);
WORD graphic 1 (additional graphics such as slashing effect);
WORD graphic 2 (character body graphic);
DWORD physique judgment_all (2.5BYTE) + TC command (1.5BYTE);
BYTE hit guard jump [40: next line (jump after hit stop)] [80: next line (without HS), 8X: jump to line X (no HS)];
BYTE Cancel [40: SA, 20: Special Move, 08: TC, 02: Dash, 01: High Jump];
WORD movement fine adjustment, graphic 3, line jump (refer to repeated hit cancellation);
};
/ * ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ * /
struct motion (24BYTE)
{
BYTE frame;
BYTE jump flag etc .;
WORD sound (1.5BYTE) + graphic inversion (0.5BYTE);
WORD graphic 1 (additional graphics such as slashing effect);
WORD graphic 2 (character body graphic);
DWORD physique judgment_all (2.5BYTE) + TC command (1.5BYTE);
BYTE hit guard skip line [80: next line, 8X: jump to line X];
BYTE Cancel [40: SA, 20: Special Move, 08: TC, 02: Dash, 01: High Jump];
WORD Graphic 3 (projectiles, other effects);
WORD zoom;
WORD Opponent action specification (used when throwing);
WORD movement fine adjustment;
BYTE jump? ;
BYTE;
};
